data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Perfect Holiday SALE! Feeling cramped in your house with all your family for the holiday? Time for an upgrade!!  Back on the market! Buyers financing fell through, HOME appraised at $389,900.00  Welcome to this lovely 3 bed 2.5 bath home in the Pines of Wekiva! This home is light and bright with high ceilings, lots of windows. Carpet upstairs & in all bedrooms. The kitchen is open to the family room with sliding glass doors leading out to the screened lanai overlooking the backyard. The grassy green backyard is the true crowning gem of this home, enjoy the Florida sunshine from your screened lanai with lovely pond views. The spacious master suite is on the first floor with private access to the lanai and a large en suite with a dual sink vanity garden tub and separate shower. Upstairs your will find 2 additional bedrooms and a bathroom. ROOF IS 2013, AC 2016 , WATER HEATER IS 2008. Located in a great Central Florida location just minutes from 441 & 429. Schedule your showing today! FULL HOUSE SOLAR POWERED. Power bill $10-$20 per month!
